Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚少年  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.35,0:00:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从神秘少女C.C.处得到了特殊的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以对任何人物下达命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让对方绝对服从的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了妹妹娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修计划将布里塔尼亚帝国毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他的朋友枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.97,0:00:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在帝国内部逐渐确立自己的立足点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这一时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前方的命运或许已经注定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 8
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次去东京租界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修也来就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜在旅馆就让一切成为既成事实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和喜欢的男生互诉衷肠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会长你有这样的对象么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河口地区布里塔尼亚的观光客很多\N治安很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会像贫民区一样可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:02:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次不会扔下你不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快进来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始这里就是我们的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以理解为这是你愿意和我们合作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我们是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么弄到这东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我拜托了一下就送给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从放荡的贵族那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会被抓住把柄的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  还有两楼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这车子不会太大了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但反过来说  这样可能反而会成为军队盘查的盲点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还附带电视
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现场情况现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  这里是河口会议中心宾馆前方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:04:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宾馆劫持犯人自称是日本解放战线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目前他们把以詹姆斯议长为中心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[Sakuradite：产于富士山附近的稀有金属，帝国侵略战争的导火索]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Sakuradite分配会议的与会人员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,观光者  以及数名工作人员作为人质
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是犯人送来的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除了詹姆斯议长等人以外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还能看到学生的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,学生会的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,犯罪集团的首领自称草壁中校\N是旧日本军人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,制造高温超电导体必不可少的材料Sakuradite
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是直接影响到世界安全保障的重要战略物质
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,11区这里是世界最大的Sakuradite的产地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在全部供给量中已达总数的70%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每年在这里举办的Sakuradite生产国会议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会决定Sakuradite的国际分配比率
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说这个结果关系到我们布里塔尼亚\N和从属国家的力量平衡也不为过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖份子很有可能是瞄准了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关系到国际舆论的该会议的被关注度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:05:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才做出这次挟持宾馆的暴行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是日本解放战线的草壁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我们日本的独立解放而站了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位虽然不是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但却是布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是支配我们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们乖乖听话就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,否则
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开始行动了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可是日本最大的反布里塔尼亚势力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不甘示弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,针对我们的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该高兴还是该悲伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会和敌方玉碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,利瓦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请在信号音后留言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种时候他在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连接宾馆的桥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只留下了最主要那条\N其他都吊起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从上空和水下的接近全部失败
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了执行人质救出作战剩下的道路只剩下一条
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:06:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,延伸至会议中心宾馆最下方的逃生道路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果使用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将地基破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让宾馆沉入水中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个隧道是为了必要时运送物资
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而Sutherland也可以通过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方肯定也会有所准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但不会有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从以往他们所使用的武器水平来看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全可以回避
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉到敌影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和预想一致  从地下空洞进入了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雷光  第二启动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,左右四连脚部固定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超电磁流散弹重炮  电压确认
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,预计会有反KnightMare来福枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,散开逐个突破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超电磁流散弹重炮  发射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一击就成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真有效啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雷光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,领教了没有 布里塔尼亚的猪们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全灭?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:06:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人设置了用Glasgow改造的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像是特制加农炮的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说突破是不可能的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照要求把政治犯给释放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让恐怖份子看到我们的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是由菲米娅大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事他们应该还没有觉察到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被他们知道人质中有由菲米娅大人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会来找我们交涉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只是去旁听会议
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以名单上没有她的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定会顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我可不是保护者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们特派不能参加救出作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然提出了申请
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和他们的命令系统不同  不是正规军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能把作战交给11区住民来做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅殿下是严格区分布里塔尼亚人和编号住民的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所做的还不足以让她接受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底为了什么才有名誉布里塔尼亚人制度的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这位父亲  莎莉小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西放在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那里那里  驾驶席那边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  放在这里的盒子怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是去观光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明还是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却被恐怖份子无差别地…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的女儿没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子什么坏事都没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了与布里塔尼亚作战必须要有组织
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是如果放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照科奈莉娅的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会无视人质的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么她按兵不动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人质会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有放任布里塔尼亚人这么下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个分配给大家好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  虽然我是觉得很帅啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们是反抗组织
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是反抗组织
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正义的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特别狙击小队到达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现场保持
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各小队长进行通报确认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人质中的学生是学生会的那些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交涉还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是组织的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起个人的感情来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要优先组织的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塞希尔小姐  那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道  想把人质
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是对我们的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然没有任何回应的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每30分钟我们会推一个人下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了人质  期待你们会有诚意的回应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然杀人示众  那些野蛮人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们退一步交涉  让他们先放了妇女儿童
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦我们退让了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就代表认同了恐怖份子的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就强攻突破
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不也要确保了由菲米娅大人的安全之后才能做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总督  ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO联络我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三号车被ZERO给夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉姆森在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说是回过神来的时候已经被开走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么现在那辆三号车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在军队的正中间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经确认了  是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,需要狙击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保持那个状态待机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,包围完成后把他逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  他所说的正义到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在此之前可能会被杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,后面的大家也没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们不是用那辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以把自己的基地开出来给人家看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以相信他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫ZERO的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我早说了他很可疑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过万一出了什么事我会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我想在这里回报你上次的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是利用你的时候还早得很
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果像预想的一样就不需要使用Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又见面了ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是日本解放战线的成员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说想要协助他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在要以我们的事优先
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遗弟克洛维斯的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在这里报
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅  你选择哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死了的克洛维斯和活着的由菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个条件已经确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子没变啊  科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你从很早之前开始就一直溺爱由菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你无法行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感情拖住了你的后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由我来救出由菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:11:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会救给你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚来的联络
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通传所有部队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让ZERO通过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让ZERO通过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本解放战线会把我当作同志来接受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是当作妨碍者来处理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是不可能抵抗住想见ZERO这个诱惑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作战的前置条件全部确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:44.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办  总督
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为ZERO过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们杀死下一个人质的时间应该稍有推迟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  这就是好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,包括ZERO一网打尽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您的指名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以出击了 Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说是要从隧道里面向着敌人堆里冲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是说要把我们当成诱饵来制造破绽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好像亲卫队要趁着混乱突破
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说好像  这种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塞希尔  我要干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对于能够救出大家的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我和这架Lancelot是需要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就应该干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便那是诱饵也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木准尉  现在说明作战概要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通过基础探测
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人质都在宾馆的中间层
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被关在食物储藏室里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向导兵器  Z-01  Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要使用逃生通道的隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,移动到宾馆附近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到达之后  破坏宾馆的地基
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让宾馆沉入水中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,预计8分钟就可以接触到人质所在位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人质的救出及恐怖份子的清除由其他部队负责
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另外为了破坏地基需要使用VARIS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[VARIS：Variable Ammunition Repulsion Impact \NSpitfire，手持来福枪,泛用弹药斥力冲击炮]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用反器械冲击子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,设定为3级
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,问题就在于隧道内埋伏着的凑热闹的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由于空间被限定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以即使Lancelot的回避率也只有47.8%
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你要在适当的时机回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能弄坏Lancelot呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,适当的时机?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星期天我要和会长还有妮娜去河口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 那天我有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  谢谢你邀请我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作战开始还有12分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,进入倒计时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,11…区人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然说11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们知道了啦  所以请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快更正你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会更正的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你那算什么口气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来隔壁房间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好教教你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快站起来  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我和你们的首领见面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊  副总督
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是布里塔尼亚第三皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅·Li·布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想和我联手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就让我们看看你的真面目  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样很无礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在此之前我想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在此次行动的最后  希望得到怎样的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不言而喻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要让国内外都知道日本人还没有倒下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真陈腐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们思想真陈腐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无可救药了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什么意思  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,MVS Booster
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancelot  出发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确认反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方KnightMare  一架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,移动速度约为普通的两倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  反正都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超电磁流散弹重炮发射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不是说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就不是诱饵而是想好好干一场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请报告中校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才联络时说的人质带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自称是由菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO  我和你没有话可说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:16:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校他们自行了断了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟到自己行动的毫无意义之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了民众你自愿站出来当人质吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  特派的KnightMare
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  照这个进度应该可以突破
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以期待他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  如果是这个破坏力的话还可以承受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第五发都被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要胆怯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四连全部展开炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可是绝对防卫圈 一定要死守
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塞希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里我要使用VARIS了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  那很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滑行领域很窄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早就有这个觉悟要赌一场了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说你就任副总督的位子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是值得高兴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  因为克洛维斯死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被我杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最后他还向我祈求饶他一命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用下令杀死11区住民的那张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你杀死哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是布里塔尼亚皇帝的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能量全开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使之后炮身融掉也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要确保日升旗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候的白色机体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊  枢木准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三号摄像机怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是被ZERO拿走了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想要反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是为了摄像机才抢走的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了利用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没能救成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被关在宾馆里的人质全都救出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.22,0:20:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,返还给你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢说如此厚颜无耻的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说如果敢对你出手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你会抢回人质的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬畏我们  追求我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的名字是  黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骑士团?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:21:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖份子自称骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是所有手无寸铁之人的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是11区住民
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本解放战线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用卑劣的手段把布里塔尼亚人当作人质
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,残酷地杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是无意义的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们进行了制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说不能这样播放
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,责任?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西由我来负担
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛维斯前总督也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下令虐杀手无寸铁的11区住民
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能眼睁睁看着这种残虐的行为不管
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此对他进行了制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不否定战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,强者单方面杀害弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是绝对不能允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有权利开枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.85,0:21:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那些有被射杀的觉悟的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.42,0:21:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在有力量的人攻击无力量的人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会再次出现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕那敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有多么强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正义的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有力量之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畏惧我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.48,0:22:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无力之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,追求我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世界由我们黑色骑士团来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仲裁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.73,0:23:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来临了  天助我力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.71,0:23:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到能把科奈莉娅的弱点抓来当人质
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:23:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅这个弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:24:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  这里就是黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的反击
